Nutrient data for: RAW STUFFED CHICKEN BREASTS WITH RIB MEAT, UPC: 073461905085

CHICKEN BREAST WITH RIB MEAT (CONTAINING UP TO 13% OF A SOLUTION OF WATER, RICE STARCH, LEMON JUICE CONCENTRATE, VINEGAR, SALT, ROAST CHICKEN, SUGAR, ONION POWDER, NATURAL FLAVORING), BUTTER (CREAM, MILK, SALT, ANNATTO [COLOR]), ENRICHED BLEACHED WHEAT FLOUR (NIACIN, REDUCED IRON, THIAMIN MONONITRATE, RIBOFLAVIN, FOLIC ACID), PASTEURIZED PROCESS SWISS AND AMERICAN CHEESE (SWISS CHEESE [CULTURED MILK AND SKIM MILK, SALT, ENZYMES], AMERICAN CHEESE [CULTURED MILK, SALT, ENZYMES], CREAM, SODIUM PHOSPHATE, SALT), WATER, DEHYDRATED POTATO (POTATOES, MONO & DIGLYCERIDES). CONTAINS LESS THAN 2% OF THE FOLLOWING: MODIFIED FOOD STARCH, SPICE, YELLOW CORN FLOUR, CANOLA OIL, GARLIC POWDER, SUGAR, YEAST, DEXTROSE, PARSLEY, SALT, YELLOW 5 (COLOR), SOYBEAN OIL, YELLOW 6 (COLOR). PREBROWNED IN VEGETABLE OIL. Date available: 05/25/2018 Date last updated by company: 05/25/2018
